# 015: Project Structure Standards

## 1. Root Directory Structure

**Permitted Root Files:**
- `README.md`, `LICENSE`, `pyproject.toml`, `pdm.lock`, `docker-compose.yml`
- `.gitignore`, `.pdm-python`, `.dockerignore`, `AGENTS.md`

